title: Star Jim v1.1.4
description:
STAR JIM HELP! Only you can save us!

The stars have fallen from heaven, condemning the Universe to extinction in the vacuum. Rescue all stars, return the constellations in place for the Universe to shine again, and ....

SAVE THE WORLD!

Avoid the enemies and collect the stars that make up each constellation.
Picking the brightest star every time, you get a special bonus at the end of each level.

Features:

More then 100 different levels.
Amazing gameplay and addictiveness
Simple controls.

What's new in version 1.1.4

Minor bugs fixed.
